Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.80,0:02:43.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你能杀了他们吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.34,0:02:45.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是 奈落大人
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.31,0:02:50.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,犬夜叉 弥勒 还有珊瑚
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.18,0:02:54.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是 奈落大人
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.65,0:02:59.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被窃取的铁碎牙 决战 奈落之城！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.89,0:03:04.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为我让他忘记了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.93,0:03:07.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,琥珀所有的记忆
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.93,0:03:15.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把犬夜叉的刀铁碎牙抢来
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.94,0:03:19.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么我就让琥珀永远活下去
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.91,0:03:25.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.21,0:03:27.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我到底在做什么
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.72,0:03:36.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,珊瑚 怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.96,0:03:39.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没什么…刚刚睡醒了而已
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.23,0:03:45.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我会杀了他…虽然觉得很对不起你
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.63,0:03:48.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我说过了 那个人根本不是琥珀
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.27,0:03:49.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是琥珀的话
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.34,0:03:51.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是我弟弟的话
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.47,0:03:54.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,根本不可能做出杀死村民的暴行
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.91,0:03:57.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我一定要…把他跟奈落一起除掉
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.75,0:04:05.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有这么简单吗…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.69,0:04:08.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他的容貌没有任何变化
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.76,0:04:12.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真能轻易的憎恨他 忘了他的一切吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.19,0:04:13.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别小看我
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.36,0:04:15.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我可是除妖师
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.26,0:04:18.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么可能落入这种卑劣的圈套里
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.30,0:04:20.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,换做是我的话
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.27,0:04:23.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可能也下不了手吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.01,0:04:28.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为容貌丝毫没有改变
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.98,0:04:33.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以是无法憎恨或遗忘的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.52,0:04:40.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,犬夜叉说的是桔梗吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.85,0:04:41.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,犬夜叉
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.66,0:04:45.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别大意 我们被包围了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.82,0:05:10.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,琥珀…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.32,0:05:16.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 弥勒！你想做什么
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.39,0:05:18.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的风穴还没完全康复呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.76,0:05:20.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊…可是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.99,0:05:21.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快住手 弥勒
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.40,0:05:24.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别为了那些杂碎去送死
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.56,0:05:27.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里只要由我来干掉头目就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.78,0:05:39.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,杂碎给我滚开！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.53,0:06:00.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这种程度的力量也想跟我交手吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.87,0:06:07.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,死吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.44,0:06:10.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行 不能杀他
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.31,0:06:17.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶！可恶可恶 ！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.89,0:06:21.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我太心软了 实在太心软了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.46,0:06:23.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,杀了他就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.89,0:06:25.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是奈落的圈套
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.83,0:06:27.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我非杀了这小子不可啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.40,0:06:31.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没错…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.47,0:06:33.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,像我这种人 死了算了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.83,0:06:34.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.34,0:06:35.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.90,0:06:38.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都是我杀的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.84,0:06:41.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爸爸 伙伴 还有村人们
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.91,0:06:43.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,全部都是我杀死的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.91,0:06:48.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以 像我这种人…死了算了…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.42,0:07:00.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂…你干什么？你想怎么样？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.87,0:07:06.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那孩子想把四魂碎片取出来
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.30,0:07:09.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以才弄伤自己的背部
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.17,0:07:11.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,维系着琥珀性命的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.61,0:07:14.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是埋在他体内的四魂碎片
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.61,0:07:16.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果把它取出来的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.01,0:07:19.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,琥珀立刻就会死的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.69,0:07:28.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,住手！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.04,0:07:43.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,珊瑚…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.97,0:07:45.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,珊瑚
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.64,0:07:46.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,珊瑚
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.54,0:07:48.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在做什么 珊瑚
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.72,0:08:06.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他在试探我吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.49,0:08:11.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想看我能不能亲手送上铁碎牙吗…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.37,0:08:15.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我…我…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.01,0:08:23.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,云母
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.74,0:08:25.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等一下 珊瑚
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.01,0:08:27.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你想做什么啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.25,0:08:31.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我只能这么做了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.02,0:08:34.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我唯一能办到的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.76,0:08:37.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的本意是…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.34,0:08:50.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,走吧 犬夜叉
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.47,0:08:53.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了？犬夜叉 还有弥勒法师
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.77,0:08:55.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么样 犬夜叉
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.31,0:08:58.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还没消失 那小鬼的…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.14,0:09:02.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,琥珀的血腥味还残留着 一直闻的到
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.25,0:09:04.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是奈落在引诱我们吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.19,0:09:09.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,风穴被封印 铁碎牙又被夺走
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.19,0:09:13.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,管他的 我还有这双拳头！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.84,0:09:30.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这座城是…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.82,0:09:37.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,琥珀
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.32,0:09:39.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,琥珀
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.59,0:09:44.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,先将飞来骨放下来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.09,0:09:45.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奈落…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.84,0:10:02.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,辛苦你了 珊瑚
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.31,0:10:07.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你遵照约定把犬夜叉的刀 铁碎牙带来了是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.85,0:10:09.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让我见琥珀
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.32,0:10:13.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后我才会把刀给你
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.03,0:10:23.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奈落 现在马上把琥珀变回原来的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.76,0:10:26.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,即使把我杀了也无济于事
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.13,0:10:29.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不可能不清楚这些的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.37,0:10:32.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一切都是四魂之玉造成的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.14,0:10:38.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想要四魂碎片的妖怪 袭击了你的村子
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.65,0:10:44.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你父亲的死 琥珀徘徊在生与死之间
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.35,0:10:46.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都是四魂之玉的因果
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.42,0:10:48.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,少胡说八道
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.66,0:10:50.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是你杀害了父亲与伙伴
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.39,0:10:53.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只因为你想要四魂之玉的力量…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.53,0:10:55.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家就被你杀害了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.80,0:11:01.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人因四魂之力而生 亦因四魂之力而死
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.77,0:11:05.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要厌恶四魂之玉
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.01,0:11:09.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,琥珀就是依靠它的力量生存着的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.28,0:11:16.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,依照约定 是用刀换琥珀吧 怎么办？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.68,0:11:19.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,卑鄙无耻 什么约定啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.32,0:11:22.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这就是我的答案 接招吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.44,0:11:41.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.84,0:11:43.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个城的少主
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.58,0:11:45.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,荫刀是个宅心仁厚的主君
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.35,0:11:49.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他慎重地埋葬了除妖师的骸骨
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.45,0:11:51.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.58,0:11:55.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,派人去保护你的 也是我呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.46,0:11:56.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你杀了他吗 ！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.62,0:12:03.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人见荫刀…现在我就是城主 荫刀了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.60,0:12:04.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,混蛋！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.37,0:12:07.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,死吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.02,0:12:27.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,云母
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.99,0:12:33.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,云母 你怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.09,0:12:37.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有比我的瘴气更毒的东西了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.40,0:12:39.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,珊瑚 你也一样
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.90,0:12:41.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.65,0:12:58.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么样 愿意跟琥珀一起在这城中侍奉我吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.92,0:13:03.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,荫刀也说过呢 叫你回到城中
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.93,0:13:12.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,少给我胡说八道 除掉你才是我的本意
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.77,0:13:15.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为了父亲和伙伴的仇恨 我要杀了你
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.17,0:13:19.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,琥珀 过来
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.97,0:13:48.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再见了 姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.20,0:13:50.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,琥珀…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.17,0:13:53.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看到城了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.94,0:13:54.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是这里
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.48,0:13:57.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这就是奈落的城吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.08,0:14:00.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是珊瑚的声音
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.25,0:14:01.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.33,0:14:20.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,琥珀…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.83,0:14:22.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,琥珀 快醒过来
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.27,0:14:54.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没错 珊瑚
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.54,0:14:56.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,杀了他吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.27,0:14:59.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,用那双手杀了弟弟
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.11,0:15:05.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后只需渴望 渴望自己能生存下去
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.18,0:15:08.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只想让自己得到救赎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.05,0:15:13.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你杀了琥珀 染上鲜血之时
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.79,0:15:17.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,四魂碎片就能增加黑暗之光
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.29,0:15:24.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,四魂之光正因为其污浊 才更美丽
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.31,0:15:35.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呵…怎么可能…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.58,0:15:38.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我怎么可能下得了手杀你
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.65,0:15:47.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我…下不了手…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.66,0:15:52.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,琥珀…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.10,0:16:05.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,姐姐…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.68,0:16:09.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,珊瑚
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.38,0:16:10.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,珊瑚
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.98,0:16:12.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,云母 你没事吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.02,0:16:25.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是被弟弟所伤吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.86,0:16:27.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太过分了…为何做出这种事
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.23,0:16:30.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奈落…你在哪 滚出来！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.53,0:16:34.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,杀害父亲与同伴的弟弟
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.60,0:16:37.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,姐姐却无法取其性命
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.65,0:16:41.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,弟弟比她自己的生命更重要
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.46,0:16:47.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为何能达到如此境界 我实在想不通
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.15,0:16:56.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,琥珀
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.16,0:17:01.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只差一点 只差一点就能恢复意识了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.26,0:17:05.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,犬夜叉 这不是跟你当年的情况一样吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.93,0:17:07.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跟50年前的你…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.17,0:17:08.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你说什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.54,0:17:14.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让珊瑚憎恨弟弟 让她亲手杀了他
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.67,0:17:18.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如此 他背上的四魂碎片就会沾染邪气
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.68,0:17:21.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这和让彼此信赖的桔梗与犬夜叉互相憎恨
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.81,0:17:23.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,自相残杀的圈套一样
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.42,0:17:27.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不可饶恕 我绝对无法饶恕这样的事
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.92,0:17:32.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就像桔梗为了不让四魂之玉被污染而死去一样
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.99,0:17:37.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,珊瑚也…没有与弟弟交战
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.20,0:17:41.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奈落那家伙真愚蠢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.83,0:17:44.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,珊瑚怎么可能会做出那种事
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.51,0:17:49.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为珊瑚…是个爱护弟弟的好姐姐啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.68,0:17:56.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 是瘴气！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.42,0:17:58.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,肤浅的家伙们
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.72,0:18:01.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,淹没在瘴气之海中吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.47,0:18:17.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过父亲说了哦 琥珀的功夫越来越好了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.97,0:18:18.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.94,0:18:19.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.01,0:18:22.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我还是第一次被父亲夸奖呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.18,0:18:25.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有点不好意思呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.25,0:18:28.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,珊瑚 你还不能乱动…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.02,0:18:30.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,珊瑚 你别乱动了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.25,0:18:33.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等会我还有一大堆怨言跟你说呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.19,0:18:35.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你可别死掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.22,0:18:37.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都是我害的…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.92,0:18:43.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.07,0:18:50.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.01,0:19:03.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对了！奈落…那家伙拥有四魂碎片
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.42,0:19:05.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是那个
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.79,0:19:09.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奈落！觉悟吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.73,0:19:22.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.10,0:19:28.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奈落…你真是太差劲
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.74,0:19:32.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这女人…这种力量是怎么回事…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.95,0:19:36.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,将邪念 瘴气和毒气都一扫而空
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.05,0:19:40.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这种力量是桔梗的…难道…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.39,0:19:43.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算你求饶我也不会原谅你的！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.23,0:19:53.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这的确就是桔梗的破魔矢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.47,0:19:55.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么这丫头是…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.37,0:19:57.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,射中了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.14,0:20:00.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好厉害 它穿透瘴气把奈落射穿了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.88,0:20:05.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,戈薇
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.48,0:20:09.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,千万不能放开云母哦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.52,0:20:12.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,琥珀
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.49,0:20:15.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,琥珀
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.36,0:20:18.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,琥珀！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.55,0:20:45.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,城消失了…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.65,0:20:47.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原来那是城的幻影
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.09,0:20:50.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,犬夜叉
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.40,0:20:59.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奈落逃走了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.03,0:21:03.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯…因为四魂碎片消失了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.54,0:21:05.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.64,0:21:09.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起 我没能干掉奈落
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.61,0:21:12.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不用自责 若没有戈薇小姐的话
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.08,0:21:15.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们大家早就没命了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.08,0:21:21.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,戈薇 好像刚才的你是目前为止最强的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.62,0:21:25.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,犬夜叉…绝对要打倒奈落哦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.06,0:21:29.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,无论多么艰难 大家都要同心协力
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.96,0:21:32.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行啦 珊瑚 不能乱动啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.87,0:21:33.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,珊瑚
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.13,0:21:37.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快点阻止她 珊瑚好像想走掉
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.70,0:21:41.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到底 你想去什么地方呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.97,0:21:45.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起 我已无法跟大家在一起了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.75,0:21:51.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,珊瑚 大家都知道你是因为弟弟才被奈落欺骗的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.85,0:21:52.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,正因如此
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.75,0:21:54.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我还会再背叛的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.15,0:21:57.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要琥珀还在奈落手里的话
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.89,0:21:58.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,珊瑚…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.96,0:22:03.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,珊瑚 你打算一个人去讨伐奈落吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.16,0:22:06.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只能这么做了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.60,0:22:10.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么可以…让大家一起去救你的弟弟吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.77,0:22:13.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奈落不是你一个人能对付的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.61,0:22:18.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来吧 首先得包扎伤口
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.48,0:22:20.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们 为什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.48,0:22:24.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你唧唧歪歪的吵死了 大家在一起就是比较好啦
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.22,0:22:26.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且你也蛮会打架的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.92,0:22:28.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,犬夜叉…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.92,0:22:32.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,连轻易被夺走铁碎牙的犬夜叉都这么说了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.13,0:22:34.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如何？应该没有问题了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.53,0:22:37.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么说的好像是我很呆啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.80,0:22:39.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是说你心胸宽大哦
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.07,0:22:42.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,珊瑚讨厌我们大家吗
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.14,0:22:46.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为我的缘故 使大家遭受这种危险
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.97,0:22:51.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,往后可能还会重蹈覆辙…但是
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.45,0:23:01.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,珊瑚…一直都很痛苦吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.19,0:23:06.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已经不要紧了 珊瑚
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.29,0:23:08.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为有大家陪着你
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.80,0:23:18.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\4c&H77D68D&\3c&H244D2C&\4a&H00&\c&HC1D4C8&}我们在生命的旅程中
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.80,0:23:24.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\4c&H77D68D&\3c&H244D2C&\4a&H00&\c&HC1D4C8&}逐渐失去一切
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.77,0:23:30.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\4c&H77D68D&\3c&H244D2C&\4a&H00&\c&HC1D4C8&}仍坚信并追逐着光明
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.77,0:23:37.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\4c&H77D68D&\3c&H244D2C&\4a&H00&\c&HC1D4C8&}现在与你一同启航
